The,service,enhances,the,provider,s,online,learning,and,training,platform,by,allowing,creation,of,content,combining,text,images,audio,and,video,It,also,allows,creation,of,tests,and,quizzes,including,multiple,question,types,with,specified,answers,API,methods,support,management,of,navigation,within,the,platform,s,resources,and,tracking,of,learners,user,accounts,with,full,contact,information,and,history,of,interaction,with,the,service,Methods,support,creation,and,arrangement,of,learning,objects,such,as,instructional,text,and,media,elements,along,with,assessments,of,learner,progress,The,API,can,generate,notifications,and,comments,to,learners,and,application,managers,as,well,as,reports,on,learner,progress,and,system,activity